N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4003.48 - Prices of admission

State Regulations

The commission shall fix, within the limitations
prescribed by law, the prices of admission to race tracks and to special
enclosures and reserved spaces therein. Notes
